\subsection{Investment}

Money may be invested into the bank with a 50\% return (150\% increase) before collecting a certain “Passing Through Go” amount after a full loop is completed.\\
\\
\
\texttt{Additional Situation:
}\\
\
\text{If one goes bankrupt or goes to jail, only half the invested money can be taken out.}


\subsection{Miscellaneous Modifications}
\begin{outline}
    \1 Bid for start order - start at \$10
    \1 If you roll 2 doubles then pay \$100
    \2 \textbf{However, when rolling 2 ones the player receives \$100}
    \1 All fees from Chance and Community Chest go to the "Free Parking" pot
    \2 Next player who lands on free parking collects sum of payments
    \1 When player lands on community chess or chance take 2 cards 
\1 Decrease starting amount from \$1500 to \$750

\end{outline}
